  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  adult patients, &gt;=18 years of age;

          -  histologically confirmed adenocarcinoma of the colon or rectum, with metastatic
             disease;

          -  &gt;=1 measurable lesion;

          -  ECOG performance status of &lt;=1.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  prior systemic therapy for advanced or metastatic disease;

          -  adjuvant or neo-adjuvant treatment for non-metastatic disease in past 6 months;

          -  other malignancy within past 5 years, except cured basal cell cancer of skin or cured
             cancer in situ of cervix;

          -  clinically significant cardiovascular disease in past 6 months.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
